{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1740205376.90887","card_id":"Q_12935897562","target":{"id":12935897562,"title":"大连一国企被曝要求不献血的人交 100 元，负责人称「系表述有误，导致员工误解」，事情真相如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/12935897562","type":"question","created":1740129456,"answer_count":374,"follower_count":677,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5582,6391,9740,27572],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，辽宁大连一网友在社交平台爆料称，自己所在部门发布通知，“不献血的人要交100元，成功献血的人将获得4200元补助和3天休假！”“ 全部门300多人，献血名额只有7个。” 2月21日，记者联系当地献血中心了解情况，“鼓励无偿献血，交钱和补助都属于该公司个人行为，后续会让相关部门人员去沟通一下。” 记者还联系到该企业工会人员，其称系表述有误，导致员工误解，互助金非强制缴纳，献血名额也无限制，鼓励大家多去。“每个人交100块钱，给献血员工一个互助的补贴补助，不是强制的。” 资料来源大连一国企被曝要求不献血的人交100元，当地献血中心：属于该公司个人行为_补助_胡盛龙_部门"},"attached_info":"CkIIur705LPG8MJXEAMaCTExMzU2MjY5NyCwieG9BjAAOKUFQAByCzEyOTM1ODk3NTYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"466 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-29a824cfe89dc1bc602a269e75f874f7_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1740205376.92577","card_id":"Q_351874821","target":{"id":351874821,"title":"哪吒的母亲是李靖原配，为什么大家称她为殷夫人而不是李夫人？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/351874821","type":"question","created":1571708444,"answer_count":229,"follower_count":330,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5753,5823,16927,154582,156312],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Iur705LPG8MJXEAMaCDQwNDcyNTc5IJy8ue0FMAA4ygJAAXIJMzUxODc0ODIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"437 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b4a4f5046ab68bdac79297141269b91f_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1",