在没有文件许可的情况下免费修建了一个水坝。” 他们用牙齿啃断树木，再混合树枝、泥巴等材料，短短1- 2天就把水坝建成了。当地动物学家表示，在修筑水坝方面，政府根本就不是河狸的对手，“河狸一晚就能建好一座水坝，最多两晚。而人类必须获得建筑许可并筹集资金，当然一个挖土机工人独自动手的话，可能花一周就能完成。” 更值得一提的是，河狸们堤坝的选址与专家为保护区规划的地点一致！捷克自然与景观保护局中波希米亚州办事处的主任说：“比我们在纸上设计得还好”。"},"attached_info":"CkEIur705LPG8MJXEAMaCTExMzQwNzc3MCDtgLi9BjAAOGlAA3ILMTIxNTkzMTk3OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"329 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5862034b15c76ef71445b93d41318f2e_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1740205376.94686","card_id":"Q_4987072286","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":4987072286,"title":"为什么现在年轻人都不怎么换手机了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4987072286","type":"question","created":1732415206,"answer_count":1052,"follower_count":1441,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[488,12706],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"为什么"},"attached_info":"CkEIur705LPG8MJXEAMaCTExMTk3NDA4NCDmnYq6BjAAOKELQARyCjQ5ODcwNzIyODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"258 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-78617daceedb9e7402d5cc1932f48dc6_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1740205376.95131","card_id":"Q_12966983763","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":12966983763,"title":"《哪吒2》票房破 130 亿，位列全球影史票房榜第 8 位，能否冲击全球影史前三？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/12966983763","type":"question","created":1740152465,"answer_count"